Costa Said ECB Was Only One Doing the Right Crisis Solving Work

-- B y   J o a o   L i m a
-- 
2011-10-21T10:54:58Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-21/costa-said-ecb-was-only-one-doing-the-right-crisis-solving-work.html
European Central Bank Governing
Council member Carlos Costa said the bank was the only European
institution that “was doing the work it should” trying to
solve the sovereign debt crisis.
  “Politicians have to place themselves ahead of the curve and
not behind the curve,”Costa said at an event in Lisbon today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
